title: Feet First
overview: Until very recently, Terry Prince was a conduit joint insulation mechanic in the Midlands; he and wife Viv lived with his parents, and football was simply a game he enjoyed playing for the local team. But Terry's natural talent has come the attention of big-league manager Harry Turnbull, and he and Viv now find themselves trying to come to terms with a variety of novel tactics... both on and off the field!
